O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:5:"title";s:99:"Cư dân mạng bắt đầu coi mạng xã hội là nguồn tin chính, thay thế cả báo chí";s:4:"link";s:98:"http://www.techz.vn/mang-xa-hoi-la-nguon-thong-tin-lon-nhat-hien-nay-nhung-lieu-c-co-ylt48372.html";s:11:"description";s:522:"<div>(Techz.vn) X&eacute;t v&#7873; ph&#432;&#417;ng di&#7879;n ngu&#7891;n th&ocirc;ng tin, c&aacute;n c&acirc;n &#273;ang d&#7847;n d&#7883;ch chuy&#7875;n t&#7915; truy&#7873;n th&ocirc;ng th&ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng sang truy&#7873;n th&ocirc;ng x&atilde; h&#7897;i. &#272;&oacute; l&agrave; k&#7871;t lu&#7853;n c&#7911;a m&#7897;t nghi&ecirc;n c&#7913;u m&#7899;i v&#7915;a &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o v&agrave;o th&#7913; 5 v&#7915;a qua b&#7903;i trung t&acirc;m nghi&ecirc;n c&#7913;u Pew.</div>";s:7:"content";s:10836:"<div><div class="news-relation-top-detail"><label>B&agrave;i vi&#7871;t li&ecirc;n quan</label><ul><li><a href="http://www.techz.vn/it-ai-biet-duoc-rang-bieu-tuong-instagram-duoc-thiet-ke-chi-tron-ylt47960.html">&#272;i&#7873;u &iacute;t bi&#7871;t v&#7873; icon "huy&#7873;n tho&#7841;i" c&#7911;a Instagram: &#272;&#432;&#7907;c l&agrave;m trong 45 ph&uacute;t b&#7903;i m&#7897;t ng&#432;&#7901;i b&#7841;n</a></li><li><a href="http://www.techz.vn/twitter-canh-bao-nguoi-dung-ve-nan-tin-tac-ylt45569.html">Twitter c&#7843;nh b&aacute;o ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng v&#7873; n&#7841;n tin t&#7863;c</a></li><li><a href="http://www.techz.vn/5-thong-tin-ca-nhan-khong-nen-tiet-lo-du-facebook-yeu-cau-ylt48201.html">5 th&ocirc;ng tin c&aacute; nh&acirc;n Facebook "d&#7909;" b&#7841;n ti&#7871;t l&#7897;, nh&#432;ng ch&#7899; l&agrave;m theo</a></li></ul></div><p>Trung t&acirc;m n&agrave;y &#273;&atilde; kh&#7843;o s&aacute;t tr&ecirc;n 4.600 ng&#432;&#7901;i v&agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c bi&#7871;t h&#7885; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng nh&#7919;ng trang m&#7841;ng &#432;a th&iacute;ch nh&#432; Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, YouTube v&agrave; k&#7875; c&#7843; Snapchat &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7885;c tin t&#7913;c h&#7857;ng ng&agrave;y. Theo nghi&ecirc;n c&#7913;u v&#7873; m&#7843;ng tin t&#7913;c tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c trang m&#7841;ng x&atilde; h&#7897;i n&#259;m 2016, c&oacute; &#273;&#7871;n 62% d&acirc;n s&#7889; M&#7929; th&#7915;a nh&#7853;n r&#7857;ng h&#7885; t&igrave;m ki&#7871;m ho&#7863;c xem tin t&#7913;c nh&#7901; v&agrave;o c&aacute;c trang m&#7841;ng n&agrave;y.</p><p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://media.techz.vn/resize_x630x473/upload/2016/05/27/image-1464321297-mang%20xa%20hoi.jpg" alt=""></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><em>Ph&#7847;n &#273;&ocirc;ng d&acirc;n M&#7929; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng m&#7841;ng x&atilde; h&#7897;i &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7885;c tin t&#7913;c. &#7842;nh: Internet</em></span></p><p>Nh&#7919;ng trang m&#7841;ng x&atilde; h&#7897;i b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u b&#7883; &ldquo;nh&ograve;m ng&oacute;&rdquo; khi nh&#7919;ng nh&agrave; th&#7847;u c&#361; c&#7911;a Trends c&aacute;o bu&#7897;c r&#7857;ng c&aacute;c trang n&agrave;y c&oacute; v&#7867; &#273;&atilde; l&#7885;c ra nhi&#7873;u ngu&#7891;n tin &#273;&aacute;ng tin c&#7853;y khi &#273;&#259;ng t&#7843;i ch&uacute;ng l&ecirc;n Internet. Facebook ch&#7889;i b&#7887; c&aacute;o bu&#7897;c n&agrave;y nh&#432;ng sau &#273;&oacute; l&#7841;i t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng thay &#273;&#7893;i c&aacute;c c&aacute;ch th&#7913;c l&#7885;c nh&#7919;ng tin t&#7913;c &#273;ang th&#7883;nh h&agrave;nh.</p><p>Tr&ecirc;n th&#7921;c t&#7871;, &#273;&acirc;y l&agrave; l&#7847;n th&#7913; 2 Pew &#273;&atilde; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n nghi&ecirc;n c&#7913;u n&agrave;y v&#7899;i l&#7847;n &#273;&#7847;u ti&ecirc;n v&agrave;o n&#259;m 2013. C&aacute;c nh&agrave; khoa h&#7885;c &#273;&atilde; th&#7845;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n c&#7911;a c&aacute;c tr&igrave;nh duy&#7879;t m&#7841;ng x&atilde; h&#7897;i x&eacute;t v&#7873; m&#7863;t ngu&#7891;n cung c&#7845;p th&ocirc;ng tin so v&#7899;i m&#7863;t b&#7857;ng chung c&aacute;c ph&#432;&#417;ng ti&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i ch&uacute;ng. &#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t v&agrave;o l&uacute;c &#273;&oacute;, Facebook &#273;&atilde; c&oacute; nh&#7919;ng b&#432;&#7899;c chuy&#7875;n v&#432;&#7907;t b&#7853;c v&#7899;i s&#7921; nh&#7843;y v&#7885;t t&#7915; 47% l&ecirc;n 66%.</p><p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://media.techz.vn/resize_x630x473/upload/2016/05/27/image-1464321296-facebook.jpg" alt=""></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><em>Facebook c&oacute; s&#7921; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#432;&#7907;t b&#7853;c so v&#7899;i c&aacute;c trang x&atilde; h&#7897;i kh&aacute;c. &#7842;nh: Internet</em></span></p><p>Hi&#7879;n nay, Reddit c&oacute; &#273;&#7871;n 70% trong s&#7889; ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng trang n&agrave;y &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7885;c tin t&#7913;c, th&#7871; nh&#432;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng t&agrave;i kho&#7843;n c&#7911;a n&oacute; nh&#7887; h&#417;n r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u so v&#7899;i Facebook. Twitter c&#361;ng t&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921; v&#7899;i m&#7897;t n&#7917;a ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng th&uacute; nh&#7853;n r&#7857;ng h&#7885; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng nh&#7919;ng tr&igrave;nh duy&#7879;t web ho&#7863;c blog Internet &#273;&#7875; xem tin t&#7913;c nh&#432;ng nh&#7919;ng ch&#7881; s&#7889; c&#7911;a Twitter d&#432;&#7901;ng nh&#432; kh&ocirc;ng thay &#273;&#7893;i nhi&#7873;u trong su&#7889;t 3 n&#259;m qua. (t&#7915; 52% v&agrave;o n&#259;m 2013 l&ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n 59% trong n&#259;m nay).</p><p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://media.techz.vn/resize_x630x473/upload/2016/05/27/image-1464321298-twitter.png" alt=""></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><em>Twitter kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; nhi&#7873;u thay &#273;&#7893;i trong 3 n&#259;m qua. &#7842;nh: Internet</em></span></p><p>Sree Sreenivasan, chuy&ecirc;n gia v&#7873; m&#7841;ng x&atilde; h&#7897;i v&agrave; truy&#7873;n th&ocirc;ng k&#7929; thu&#7853;t s&#7889; v&agrave; c&#361;ng l&agrave; Gi&aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c truy&#7873;n th&ocirc;ng c&#7911;a B&#7843;o tang Metropolitan cho bi&#7871;t, &ldquo;T&ocirc;i kh&ocirc;ng ng&#7841;c nhi&ecirc;n m&#7845;y v&#7873; vi&#7879;c con ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;ang d&#7847;n chuy&#7875;n sang t&igrave;m ki&#7871;m hay nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ocirc;ng tin t&#7915; nh&#7919;ng tr&igrave;nh duy&#7879;t hay ph&#432;&#417;ng ti&#7879;n Internet m&agrave; h&#7885; &#273;ang s&#7917; d&#7909;ng.&rdquo;</p><p>Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, &ocirc;ng c&#361;ng chia s&#7867; r&#7857;ng, vi&#7879;c nh&#7919;ng th&ocirc;ng tin &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#259;ng t&#7843;i tr&ecirc;n m&#7841;ng x&atilde; h&#7897;i ph&#7847;n l&#7899;n l&agrave; nh&#7919;ng tin t&#7913;c m&#7897;t chi&#7873;u kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i l&agrave; &#273;i&#7873;u qu&aacute; m&#7899;i l&#7841;. Khi c&aacute;c trang blog b&ugrave;ng n&#7893; tr&ecirc;n Internet g&#7847;n 2 th&#7853;p k&#7927; tr&#432;&#7899;c, ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&#7885;c &#273;&atilde; t&#7921; th&iacute;ch nghi v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng th&#7913; ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i th&#7871; gi&#7899;i quan c&#7911;a h&#7885; v&agrave; lo&#7841;i b&#7887; nh&#7919;ng g&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng t&#432;&#417;ng th&iacute;ch. B&#7903;i l&#7869; cu&#7889;i c&ugrave;ng, ng&#432;&#7901;i s&#7917; d&#7909;ng m&#7899;i l&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i c&oacute; quy&#7873;n &#273;&#7883;nh &#273;o&#7841;t h&#7885; s&#7869; thu th&#7853;p hay b&#7887; qua nh&#7919;ng th&ocirc;ng tin n&agrave;o.</p><p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://media.techz.vn/resize_x630x473/upload/2016/05/27/image-1464321298-user.png" alt=""></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><em>Ng&#432;&#7901;i s&#7917; d&#7909;ng m&#7899;i l&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&#7883;nh &#273;o&#7841;t. &#7842;nh: Internet</em></span></p><p>Nghi&ecirc;n c&#7913;u c&#7911;a trung t&acirc;m Pew c&#361;ng cho bi&#7871;t 19% ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng LinkedIn s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ch&uacute;ng nh&#432; ngu&#7891;n tin t&#7913;c c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh v&agrave; ph&#7847;n &#273;&ocirc;ng t&agrave;i kho&#7843;n l&agrave; t&#7915; nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&atilde; t&#7889;t nghi&#7879;p cao &#273;&#7859;ng, &#273;&#7841;i h&#7885;c trong khi YouTube th&igrave; ng&#432;&#7907;c l&#7841;i. X&eacute;t v&#7873; gi&#7899;i t&iacute;nh, Facebook v&agrave; Instagram thu h&uacute;t nhi&#7873;u n&#7919; gi&#7899;i h&#417;n t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng v&#7899;i 57% v&agrave; 65%. Kh&ocirc;ng nh&#7919;ng v&#7853;y, Instagram c&ograve;n l&agrave; n&#417;i c&oacute; l&#432;&#7907;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i s&#7917; d&#7909;ng tr&#7867; tu&#7893;i nhi&#7873;u nh&#7845;t v&#7899;i 58% &ldquo;c&#432; d&acirc;n&rdquo; n&#7857;m trong &#273;&#7897; tu&#7893;i t&#7915; 18 &#273;&#7871;n 29.</p><p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://media.techz.vn/resize_x630x473/upload/2016/05/27/image-1464321297-instagram.jpg" alt=""></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><em>Instagram c&oacute; l&#432;&#7907;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i s&#7917; d&#7909;ng tr&#7867; nh&#7845;t. </em><em>&#7842;nh: Internet</em></span></p><p>&#272;&acirc;y th&#7921;c s&#7921; l&agrave; nh&#7919;ng th&ocirc;ng s&#7889; &#273;&aacute;ng lo ng&#7841;i &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i truy&#7873;n th&ocirc;ng c&#7893; &#273;i&#7875;n. Nghi&ecirc;n c&#7913;u c&#7911;a Pew c&#361;ng ch&#7881; ra r&#7857;ng, s&#7889; ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave; v&ocirc; t&igrave;nh hay h&#7919;u &yacute; nh&#7853;n th&ocirc;ng tin t&#7915; nh&#7919;ng trang m&#7841;ng x&atilde; h&#7897;i tr&ecirc;n th&#7921;c t&#7871; v&#7851;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng nh&#7919;ng ph&#432;&#417;ng ti&#7879;n truy&#7873;n th&ocirc;ng c&#361;. 39% ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng Facebook v&#7851;n xem tin t&#7913;c tr&ecirc;n TV, 15% v&#7851;n &#273;&#7885;c b&aacute;o v&agrave; 8% ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng Twitter v&#7851;n &#273;&#7885;c tin t&#7913;c t&#7915; b&aacute;o in, vv&hellip;</p><p>Tuy v&#7853;y, xu h&#432;&#7899;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng m&#7841;ng x&atilde; h&#7897;i &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7885;c tin t&#7913;c v&#7851;n s&#7869; ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c lan r&#7897;ng khi nh&#7919;ng tr&igrave;nh duy&#7879;t n&agrave;y c&agrave;ng chi&#7871;m &#432;u th&#7871; trong cu&#7897;c s&#7889;ng c&#7911;a ch&uacute;ng ta trong t&#432;&#417;ng lai.</p><p style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #808080;"><strong><em>Tham kh&#7843;o: <a href="http://mashable.com/2016/05/26/pew-news-social-media-study/#TjVhr.0xGgqF" target="_blank">Mashable</a></em></strong></span></p><div class="inner-article"><p class="cover formatted" style="background: url('http://media.techz.vn/upload/2016/05/20/image-techz-1463727157.jpg')no-repeat top left; background-size: 100%;">&nbsp;</p><h4 class="inner-tit">5 th&ocirc;ng tin c&aacute; nh&acirc;n Facebook "d&#7909;" b&#7841;n ti&#7871;t l&#7897;, nh&#432;ng ch&#7899; l&agrave;m theo</h4><p class="summary">Gi&#7889;ng nh&#432; Google, Facebook &#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng tr&ecirc;n n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng thi&#7871;t k&#7871; &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n, cung c&#7845;p d&#7883;ch v&#7909; mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; cho ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng, th&#7871; nh&#432;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i l&agrave; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng ch&iacute;nh c&#7911;a Facebook.</p><a title="5 th&ocirc;ng tin c&aacute; nh&acirc;n Facebook " href="http://www.techz.vn/5-thong-tin-ca-nhan-khong-nen-tiet-lo-du-facebook-yeu-cau-ylt48201.html">&nbsp;</a></div></div>";s:6:"author";O:16:"SimplePie_Author":3:{s:4:"name";N;s:4:"link";N;s:5:"email";s:8:"Gin Hồ";}s:4:"date";s:19:"1969-12-31 00:00:00";s:10:"enclosures";a:1:{i:0;O:19:"SimplePie_Enclosure":27:{s:7:"bitrate";N;s:8:"captions";N;s:10:"categories";N;s:8:"channels";N;s:9:"copyright";N;s:7:"credits";N;s:11:"description";N;s:8:"duration";N;s:10:"expression";N;s:9:"framerate";N;s:7:"handler";N;s:6:"hashes";N;s:6:"height";N;s:10:"javascript";N;s:8:"keywords";N;s:4:"lang";N;s:6:"length";N;s:4:"link";N;s:6:"medium";N;s:6:"player";N;s:7:"ratings";N;s:12:"restrictions";a:1:{i:0;O:21:"SimplePie_Restriction":3:{s:12:"relationship";s:5:"allow";s:4:"type";N;s:5:"value";s:7:"default";}}s:12:"samplingrate";N;s:10:"thumbnails";N;s:5:"title";N;s:4:"type";N;s:5:"width";N;}}s:7:"src_url";s:98:"http://www.techz.vn/mang-xa-hoi-la-nguon-thong-tin-lon-nhat-hien-nay-nhung-lieu-c-co-ylt48372.html";s:8:"src_name";s:54:"Cư dân mạng bắt đầu coi mạng xã hội  ...";}